@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_thqync(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = ((v1 * 0.16) - v1)
    v1 = wp.cos(0.63)
    v0 = (0.14 / wp.cos((v1 + 0.61 - tmp + 0.31)))
    v0 = wp.abs((wp.cos(v1 + 0.28) + (tmp + 0.59 * v2 + 0.75)))
    v0 = (wp.sin(0.75) + wp.cos((v0 + 0.98 * v1 + 0.76)))
    tmp = wp.exp(0.07)
    v2 = 0.98
    v0 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
